---
// The positive control: poll latency climbs with ingest rate (at fixed
// cardinality). Pairs with the flat-vs-cardinality chart to make the full point
// — latency tracks ingest, not key count. Self-contained, dependency-free; the
// client module draws every instance. Black-on-white, ASCII-style texture fills.
---

<figure class="lvi" data-lvi>
  <figcaption class="lvi-frame">
    <span class="lvi-tag">FIG — LATENCY vs INGEST</span>
    <h4 class="lvi-title">Poll latency scales with ingest rate</h4>
  </figcaption>

  <div class="lvi-plot">
    <svg class="lvi-svg" viewBox="0 0 680 380" role="img" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet"></svg>
    <div class="lvi-tip" hidden></div>
  </div>

  <p class="lvi-caption">
    Fixed key count with increasing ingest. While the live tail fits in cache
    (below ~5&nbsp;MB/s) polls are quick and past that point reads spill to object
    storage so latency climbs with every added MB/s.
  </p>

  <div class="lvi-legend">
    <span class="lvi-key"><span class="lvi-swatch" data-tex="p99"></span> p99 latency</span>
    <span class="lvi-key"><span class="lvi-swatch" data-tex="p50"></span> p50 latency</span>
    <span class="lvi-key"><span class="lvi-swatch lvi-swatch--band"></span> p50–p99 band</span>
  </div>
</figure>

<style>
  .lvi {
    --ink: #111;
    --paper: #fff;
    margin: 2.25rem 0;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--ink);
    background: var(--paper);
    font-family: var(--font-mono, ui-monospace, monospace);
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .lvi-frame { border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--ink); padding: 0.7rem 0.95rem 0.8rem; }
  .lvi-tag { font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #555; }
  .lvi-title {
    font-family: var(--font-mono, ui-monospace, monospace) !important;
    font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0.25rem 0 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .lvi-plot { position: relative; padding: 0.9rem 0.6rem 0; }
  .lvi-svg { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
  .lvi-svg text { font-family: var(--font-mono, ui-monospace, monospace); }
  .lvi-tip {
    position: absolute; pointer-events: none; background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper);
    font-size: 0.66rem; line-height: 1.35; padding: 0.3rem 0.45rem; white-space: nowrap;
    transform: translate(-50%, -115%); z-index: 2;
  }
  .lvi-caption {
    font-size: 0.78rem !important; line-height: 1.5; color: #333 !important;
    margin: 0 !important; padding: 0.7rem 0.95rem 0;
  }
  .lvi-legend {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem 1.1rem;
    padding: 0.7rem 0.95rem 0.9rem; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #333;
  }
  .lvi-key { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .lvi-swatch { width: 15px; height: 15px; border: 1.5px solid var(--ink); display: inline-block; }
  .lvi-swatch[data-tex="p99"] {
    background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, var(--ink) 0 1.5px, transparent 1.5px 4px);
  }
  .lvi-swatch[data-tex="p50"] {
    background-image: radial-gradient(var(--ink) 1px, transparent 1.2px); background-size: 4px 4px;
  }
  .lvi-swatch--band {
    border-color: #bbb;
    background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, #c4c4c4 0 1px, transparent 1px 5px);
  }
</style>

<script>
  import "./latencyVsIngest.client.ts";
</script>
